ose and reveal one at the same time. Check to see whether you've completed quests and score points, then pass your hand to the left and play a new turn. Along the way, you want to match up terrain, activate landmarks, visit cities, and (of course) fulfill quests.</p>\n\n<p>After fifteen turns, you'll have a completed map ready for adventure, and the explorer who's netted the most points wins.</p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong>Contents</strong></p>\n\n<p>116 Map Cards<br />\n5 Starting Cards<br />\n1 Map Maker Card<br />\n10 Quest Cards<br />\n2 Area Cards<br />\n5 Reference Cards<br />\n50 Exploration Cubes<br />\n4 Quest Tokens<br />\n5 Adventurer Pawns<br />\n1 Score Pad</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Final components are subject to change</li>\n</ul>\n\n","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"8505046","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__small/img/Vz-s7viK8-C7tUNVJxhzMHIuagI=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8505046.png","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__micro/img/iGdNPq3XHIhq8Aft5tOYTeIv7uc=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic8505046.png","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__square/img/agrWgIXEQe81Q8G5r3fyNrLwNys=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic8505046.png","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__tallthumb/img/Mb-PsXYNg9yCDmoh6bgqp3JJ7DE=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic8505046.png","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__previewthumb/img/-mOB5UMKsoQPOHL588a5Ls0a8tQ=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic8505046.png","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__square200/img/PveE0O8XN9jiKet-0nW874KCnWI=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic8505046.png","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg8E0rrlxCV90EKNDw__original/img/Ft-y6BjUTuBJWyEoQ5jXIFk8FD8=/0x0/filters:format(png)/pic8505046.png"},"imagepagehref":"/image/8505046/dungeons-and-dragons-edge-of-the-realms","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/CX2sMg